```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

<title>Your Drinks</title>

</head>

<body class="bg-blue-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen gap-6">

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-700">
Your Drinks
</h1>

<div class="flex gap-6 flex-wrap justify-center">

{% for drink in rewards %}

<div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow text-center">

<img src="{{ drink.Image }}" class="w-28 mx-auto">

<p class="font-semibold mt-2">
{{ drink.Name }}
</p>

</div>

{% endfor %}

</div>

<a href="/wheelofdrinks" class="bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded">
Pull Again
</a>

</body>

</html>
```
